<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Characteristic Species</h4>
	<div class="text"> <i>Brassica</i> <i>tournefortii</i>, <i>Malcolmia</i> <i>africana</i> and/or <i>Sisymbrium</i> <i>irio</i> is dominant in the herbaceous layer . </div>
</div>

		
	
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Vegetation Layers</h4>
	<div class="text">  Herbs < 1.5 m; cover is open to intermittent. </div>
</div>

		
	
<div class="allianceSection">
	 <h4 class="header">Habitats</h4>
	<div class="text"> Low level bottoms, alluvial fans, roadsides, sand dunes, lake shorelines, and washes, typically in disturbed areas. Soils are sandy to clay loam.  </div>
</div>

		
